Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和我做朋友吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然很开心 但是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.23,0:00:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明很开心 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当时的我对于藤宫同学的秘密还一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H578F6B&\an9\frx0\fry316\frz341.957\pos(958,476)}星\N期\N一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学总是孤身一人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绝不去交朋友的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还…一无所知
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fn腾祥铚谦钢笔简\blur0\bord0\c&H353639&}＃１ 「成为朋友的开始。」
Comment: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}于是呢 怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一次跟藤宫说了话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愿望实现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你一直都在说着这事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想跟她说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟她说了请跟我做朋友之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她说「虽然很开心 但是对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说将吾 这到底是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鬼知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好冷淡啊 将吾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你真的很吵耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是被婉言拒绝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是那样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是那么在意的话 直接去问她本人不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚刚一个人去屋顶了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是屋顶一直都是锁着的才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学平时是在这边吃午饭的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里不错啊 风景真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从来没来过屋顶 完全不晓得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且也没人 真是超赞的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是特等座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感冒 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚刚也在咳嗽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:33.85,PIN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星期二
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学是数学课的课代表对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我昨天忘记交作业了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能不能帮我跟老师说些好话 补交上去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看 果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说回来藤宫同学真的很冷淡耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天好凉快啊 没其他人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以在这里吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朋友一个人吃完就睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第五节课是体育啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下午的体育好乏力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不能交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是有人不让你交朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道是父母很严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘱咐你不要交朋友要好好学习？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并不是别人的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天是故意咳嗽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么没有一直那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么要道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学数学…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是因为很擅长数学才当的课代表？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道是感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我帮你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再…再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果你态度一直都那样冷淡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也不会说那种话的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然而 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然我确实在尽量避免和别人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}受到帮助却不道个谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然藤宫同学是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不做朋友也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天也一起吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是作为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天…屋顶见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在教室请不要跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了 我还想要是被拒绝的话可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.59,PIN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这样下去数学的学分就拿不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老师 现在才五月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是第一次从这时候就开始担心一个学生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}井上老师 要怎样才能放我走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我今天绝对要吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听好了长谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一般来说大家都要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那小子怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}/*（屏字）
