Comment: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}*/
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真遗憾 已经吃完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还没？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为你说要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不能先吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一起吃会觉得格外美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那接下来是 扑克牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}扑克牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说到午休就是扑克牌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一般来说是玩大富豪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an7}大富豪，又称大贫民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两个人玩不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那抽鬼牌呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个也不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那玩神经衰弱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur2}扑克牌背面朝上，找数字相同的两张
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}剩下的是 这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到头来还是五连败吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学记忆力真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学最擅长的果然是数学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算不上擅长 一直很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我数学是最烂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}值得尊敬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在家里很闲 所以只能学习了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要是在家里闲着 马上就跑出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学如果和朋友出去玩会去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卡拉OK之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}卡拉OK好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道你没去过卡拉OK吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊…对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那下次和我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个绝对不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对…对不起喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事…我也太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是有机会能去就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还吃得下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:57.63,PIN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星期四
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早知这样就买甜点来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽说看着充不了饥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听说车站附近新开了家可丽饼店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可丽饼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学也喜欢可丽饼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喜…喜欢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}巧克力奶黄味的很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我喜欢草莓鲜奶油味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}蓝莓起司味也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我和妈妈经常去一家店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那附近只有一把长椅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竞争很激烈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里如何呀 应该会有很多位子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我只是在想其他人会不会对这样的店有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并不是想一起去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我很乐意一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再说我们也不是朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然不是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那藤宫同学认为怎么样才算朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如说 聊什么话题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恋爱方面的话题之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恋爱话题！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恋爱话题啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是我现在也没有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要说在意的人…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我们不是朋友 这种话题不太合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是说呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我待会会洗的 就放在这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.88,PIN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天也好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学没怎么动筷子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天有点没食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下节是生物课来着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不妙啊 感觉会睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是没拿到学分可怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃… 我最危险的是数学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学数学很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了 不介意的话下次一起做数学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要再和我说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我做错事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我一开始就说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不能交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 想请你当这一切都没发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也会全部忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么能忘记呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学也办不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会忘记的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快乐的回忆 到星期一就会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不只是快乐的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关于亲近的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以及还想继续在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关于他们的记忆会每隔一星期被重置一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家人倒是例外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我没有与朋友一起留下的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 但是没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们还不是朋友对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…只有这个是我能够断言的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我与长谷同学留下的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全都会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叫我怎么相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:34.53,PIN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上次出这种状况还是啥时候来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学叫我不要再和她说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为自己会忘记 所以希望我也能忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这不就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被超级讨厌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 你果然是这么想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一般都会这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学啊 说明白点 很不合群嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不知道她在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底哪里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也太单纯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这有什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 说到底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}交朋友也只能试着谈谈看合不合得来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又不是靠毅力争取来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是想和她交往的话倒是另外一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学不是大家想象中那样冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很开朗 很健谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要和她说好一起吃便当
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她就会认真地等着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她是个只要好好谈谈就会让大家都会想和她做朋友的好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是个既温柔又十分坦率的好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你…你抖什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 没啥 不自觉地就
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果这才是真实的藤宫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那对于藤宫来说 你是特殊的存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这可是很大的进步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相比起你星期一那天的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都到这一步了 也只能努力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织 爸爸买蛋糕回来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 等一下就去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不是…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有…有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这时候我终于理解了藤宫同学所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}记忆会消失 藤宫同学的话语里完全没有谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与我一同度过的一星期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在藤宫同学的记忆里已经消失无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论是快乐的时光或是心灵相通的剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}全都会在星期一被重置
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要从头开始来过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正因为讨厌这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学才没有和任何人做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是没事的话 就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比谁都更想要交到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个时候我已经决定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论多少次都会重复这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如何与朋友一起度过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
